Sanity Integration Server
=========================

Run your rspec, cucumber, Test::Unit tests tests, integration and Javascript tests and other rake tasks on every branch and every commit of your project.

Features:

* Multiple project support
* Live Commandline output
* Web management tool and build status information
* Exclude branches you don't want to build
* Builds every commit since last build or the last one (when Sanity first starts)


Running
=======

Server:
    script/build_server

Web interface:
    script/server

